OL,4,CGreensill: Top civil servant failed to
OL,5,Cdeclare another job
OL,6, A former senior civil servant embroiled
OL,7, in a row over his job at Greensill
OL,8, Capital took another post without
OL,9, reporting it, it has emerged.
OL,11,FBill Crothers has come under fire for
OL,12,Fworking at the now-failed finance firm
OL,13,Fwhile still on the government payroll.
OL,15,FIt has now come to light he took on
OL,16,Fanother trustee role without seeking
OL,17,Fthe advice of the necessary committee.
OL,19,FMr Crothers apologised to the Advisory
OL,20,FCommittee on Business Appointments for
OL,21,Fwhat he called an "honest mistake".
